  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2d143eab&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FicvmTEvIjJrfmBiafD8piaiaWPUev1S9a3EgV5xHoZTr44fvqQFpGibK5BiavmwiaOWviahakTorCdzy5V7LOPqhZICqbg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p>VibeVoice 是一个开源的语音人工智能框架，专注于生成长达90分钟的多说话人对话音频，支持最多 4 个说话人，突破传统语音合成的限制。它实现了低延迟的实时文本转语音，采用高效的声学与语义编码器，确保音质与处理效率。</p>\n  <div data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" data-website=\"https://www.mdnice.com\" style=\"background-size:auto;background-attachment:scroll;padding-left:0px;font-size:16px;overflow-wrap:break-word;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-left:0px;background-repeat:no-repeat;word-spacing:0em;background-position-x:0%;background-position-y:0%;word-break:break-word;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';margin-top:0px;background-image:none;text-align:left;padding-top:0px;letter-spacing:0em;padding-bottom:0px;line-height:1.5em;margin-right:0px;background-clip:border-box;width:auto;background-origin:padding-box;margin-bottom:0px;padding-right:0px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 10px;padding-right: 0px;display: block;color: rgb(0, 150, 136);margin-top: 0.2rem;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom: 0.2rem;margin-left: auto;border-left-width: 3px;border-left-style: solid;border-left-color: rgb(0, 150, 136);\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0em;display:block;font-size:22px;line-height:1.5em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">microsoft/VibeVoice</span><span style=\"font-size: 0.58em;font-weight: normal;font-style: italic;color: graytext;display: block;text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://github.com/microsoft/VibeVoice\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/microsoft/VibeVoice</a></span></span></span></h2>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top:3px;letter-spacing:0e